# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:26
translate english gakuen_op_1_9882cd0f:

    # T "大陸にある数々の国の中でも比較的小国である『ルーンビナス』は、魔法で成り立っている国だ。"
    T "Runevinus, a comparatively small country among the numerous countries on this continent, is a country based on magic."

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:32
translate english gakuen_op_1_6026f090:

    # T "国民のほとんどは程度の差こそあるものの魔法が使え、産業も魔法を中心に回っている。"
    T "Most of the citizens can use magic to some extent, and the industries there also revolve around magic. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:38
translate english gakuen_op_1_15101393:

    # T "大陸史上、幾度となく起こった戦乱も魔法使い達の力で乗り越え、時には勝利し……。"
    T "In the history of the continent, it's survived numerous wars through the power of its magicians, and at times has been victorious.... "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:44
translate english gakuen_op_1_651347f0:

    # T "つまり、『ルーンビナス』は魔法使いの国なのだ。"
    T "In other words, Runevinus is the land of magicians. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:50
translate english gakuen_op_1_5fe09178:

    # T "魔力の強い者こそがエリートで、優秀な魔法使いは地位も高い。\n 魔法が中心。魔法こそ全て。魔法万歳。"
    T "Those with powerful magic are the elite, and skilled magicians have a high status. \n Magic is central. Magic is everything. Hurrah for magic. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:60
translate english gakuen_op_1_36f04546:

    # T "私は、そんな国のプリンセスである……、{size=+20}わけがもちろんなく。{/size} "
    T "And, the princess of this country.... *is not me, of course.*"

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:72
translate english gakuen_op_1_fa775363:

    # T "いたって普通の、自らの進路についてを悩む学生だ。"
    T "I'm a normal student, trying to decide on her course of study. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:78
translate english gakuen_op_1_19fb53ca:

    # T "（お姫様になりたいだとか、そういう現実逃避はするべきじゃないわよ……。\n 現実に生きなきゃ）"
    T "(I shouldn't be running away from reality, dreaming of being a princess...\nI've got to live in the real world.)"

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:85
translate english gakuen_op_1_3c037a23:

    # T "というわけで、私、[firstname]＝[familyname]は思いきり現実に生きていた。"
    T "And like that, I, [firstname] [familyname], live in reality as much as possible. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:91
translate english gakuen_op_1_cc35e5a3:

    # T "魔法王国だとかいうのがそもそも現実的でないとかいう意見は却下する。\n だって、舞台がそうなのだから仕方ない。"
    T "I reject the opinion that a magical kingdom is in itself unrealistic. \n
That's the setting, so I can't do anything about it. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:98
translate english gakuen_op_1_c6265461:

    # T "ここ、ルーンビナスでは、基礎教育を終えると大部分の生徒がさらなるキャリアアップを目指して進学する。\n もちろん私も、そのつもりだ。"
    T "Here in Runevinus, most students continue their studies after completing basic education. \n
Of course, I intend to do that as well. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:105
translate english gakuen_op_1_53c81d57:

    # T "ただ問題なのは……、どんな種類の学校を選ぶのか、という点。"
    T "The problem is.... what sort of school I should choose. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:118
translate english gakuen_op_1_76c24b73:

    # voice ari_g0060
    # Lorina "「駄目よ、そんな、全寮制の学校だなんて……。\n おうちから通える学校も、たくさんあるでしょう？」"
    voice ari_g0060
    Lorina "A boarding school? Don't go to one... \n
There's a lot of schools you can commute to from our house. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:126
translate english gakuen_op_1_11c682fd:

    # T "「だけど姉さん、私がいると姉さんも大変じゃない？\n 私がいなくなったら、姉さんだってもっと自由な時間を持てるはずだわ」"
    T "But nee-san, isn't it hard on you if I'm here? \n
If I'm gone, you'll have more free time. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:136
translate english gakuen_op_1_324be7cc:

    # voice ari_g0061
    # Lorina "「そんなことないわ。私は、あなた達と一緒にいるのがとても好きなのよ？\n だから心配はいらないわ」"
    voice ari_g0061
    Lorina "That's not true. I love to spend time with you. \n So you don't need to worry."

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:147
translate english gakuen_op_1_c9cab782:

    # voice ari_g0062
    # Lorina "「ふふ……、あなたはとても優しい子ね、[firstname]」"
    voice ari_g0062
    Lorina "Heh heh, you're a very kind girl, [firstname]."

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:154
translate english gakuen_op_1_1d89f351:

    # T "「…………」"
    T "\"......\""

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:160
translate english gakuen_op_1_6ed39fc7:

    # T "幼い頃に母が亡くなって以来、ずっと私と妹のために母親役を務めている姉の負担を少しでも軽くするために、私は全寮制の学校を希望していた。"
    T "I wish to attend a boarding school, in order to ease the burden on my older sister, who's acted as a mother to my younger sister and me after our mother died when I was young. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:166
translate english gakuen_op_1_02fae513:

    # T "姉がいかに彼女自身の時間を削り、私たち下の妹たちのためにどれだけ心を砕いてきたのかは知っているつもりだ。"
    T "I'm aware of how much of her time and hard work she's given to her younger sisters. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:172
translate english gakuen_op_1_8a3b7115:

    # T "そんな姉も、私が家を出ることで負担が減る分、もっと姉自身の時間を持つことができるようになるだろう。"
    T "If I leave the house, she will be able to have more time for herself. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:178
translate english gakuen_op_1_475f7736:

    # T "経済面で頼らざるを得ない父からも、全寮制の学校で構わないという許可は得ている。"
    T "My father, who I have to rely on financially, has given me permission to attend a boarding school. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:184
translate english gakuen_op_1_4ca01391:

    # T "が、それに一番真っ向から反対しているのが当の姉だった。"
    T "However, the most direct opposition is from my sister herself. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:190
translate english gakuen_op_1_52868f3d:

    # T "優しい姉は、私が彼女のために無理をして全寮制の学校に行こうとしているのではないか、と危惧しているらしいのだ。"
    T "It seems my gentle sister may have suspect that I'm forcing myself to go to a boarding school for her sake."

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:196
translate english gakuen_op_1_46d7053d:

    # T "不遇に耐える、けなげな妹。\n ……というには、あまりにも恵まれていると思うのだが。"
    T "A younger sister, gallantly enduring misfortune. \n ....Although, I think I've been fairly blessed. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:203
translate english gakuen_op_1_1c35d1b5:

    # T "（……私はそんなにいい子じゃないわ）"
    T "(...I'm not that good of girl)"

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:209
translate english gakuen_op_1_daed1133:

    # T "姉は、ある種の親馬鹿なのかもしれない。\n 彼女が私を見る目には、妹への愛情フィルターがかかってしまっているような気がする。"
    T "My sister might be that sort of overly doting parent. \n I have a feeling she looks at me though rose-colored glasses. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:219
translate english gakuen_op_1_fd5aa516:

    # voice ari_g0063
    # Lorina "「私もね、少し調べてみたのよ。\n あなたが今希望している全寮制の学校があるじゃない？」"
    voice ari_g0063
    Lorina "I've also researched a bit. The school you that to go to now is a boarding school, isn't it? "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:230
translate english gakuen_op_1_5ce8fda4:

    # voice ari_g0064
    # Lorina "「あそことそう変わらないカリキュラムで、同じことを学べる学校が近くにあるのよ。\n そっちにしたらどうかしら？」"
    voice ari_g0064
    Lorina "There's a school nearby that has pretty much the same curriculum, where you can study the same things. What about going there? "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:238
translate english gakuen_op_1_da6f5327:

    # T "穏やかな口調で提案する姉の声に、押し付けがましいようなところは一切ない。\n 思いやりを持って接してくれている。"
    T "There's nothing pushy in her voice as she suggests this gently. \n She's acting with consideration. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:245
translate english gakuen_op_1_26fcc1b0:

    # T "心優しくて、一見ふわふわとしていても、芯のしっかりとした素敵な女性。\n それが私の姉である、ロリーナ＝[familyname]だ。"
    T " Though kindly, and at the first glance soft, she's a splendid woman who has inner strength. That is my sister, Lorina [familyname]. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:252
translate english gakuen_op_1_1eeb2b58:

    # T "「でも、姉さん……」"
    T "\"But, nee-san...\""

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:261
translate english gakuen_op_1_07421f55:

    # voice ari_g0065
    # Lorina "「それとも……。\n [firstname]、もしかしてあなた……、何か家にいたくない理由でも……？」"
    voice ari_g0065
    Lorina " Then... \n [firstname], could there be... some reason you don't want to be at home...? "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:269
translate english gakuen_op_1_b58e1b83:

    # T "なおも言い募ろうとした私に、姉さんは眉尻を下げて不安そうな顔を見せた。"
    T "After I had tried to argue, my sister looked saddened and uneasy. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:275
translate english gakuen_op_1_343ac58c:

    # T "この優しい姉に、そんな顔をさせてしまったのが自分だと思うと、罪悪感に胸が締め付けられる。"
    T "Realizing that I had made my gentle sister sad, my chest tightened with guilt."

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:281
translate english gakuen_op_1_32ca2e1f:

    # T "「まさか……！\n そんなわけないわ！」"
    T "\"No way! That's not true!\""

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:288
translate english gakuen_op_1_e3499c53:

    # T "私は、家族を大事に思っている。"
    T "I care deeply about my family. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:294
translate english gakuen_op_1_0f60f43f:

    # T "ほとんど家にいない父も、妹のイーディスも、そして当然ロリーナ姉さんのことも愛している。家族でなくとも、この姉を嫌う人なんて存在しないとまで思う。"
    T " I love my father, who's rarely home, my younger sister Edith, and of course, Lorina. Family or not, I think there's no one who would dislike my sister. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:300
translate english gakuen_op_1_ce52d5f1:

    # T "ただ、ほんの少しだけ。"
    T "But, there's just one small thing. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:306
translate english gakuen_op_1_44ddeeb0:

    # T "完璧で、美しい、淑女の見本のような姉さんの傍にいることが……。\n 守られたような状況に甘んじていることが、辛いと思ってしまっただけだ。"
    T "Being next to my sister, flawless, beautiful, an ideal lady... \n
 I'm spoiled by being under her protection, but I've ended up finding it difficult. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:313
translate english gakuen_op_1_98d61559:

    # T "いたたまれなさを感じるのは贅沢な話で、私の勝手で個人的な感情だ。\n 姉に話す必要はない。"
    T "I'm fortunate be able to feel this way, so it's a selfish personal feeling. \n
 I don't need to tell this to my sister. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:323
translate english gakuen_op_1_5f5d206c:

    # voice ari_g0066
    # Lorina "「それならよかった……！\n まだ時間はあるのだもの、もうちょっと考えてみてもいいと思うわ」"
    voice ari_g0066
    Lorina "That's good then...! \n
You've still got time, so you can think it over again. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:331
translate english gakuen_op_1_595d13f5:

    # T "彼女は、私の言葉ににっこりと心から嬉しげに微笑むと、安心したように息を吐き出した。"
    T "She smiles, sincerely happy at my words, and with a sigh of relief. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:337
translate english gakuen_op_1_1172f1d2:

    # T "そんな姉を見ていると、これ以上全寮制の学校のことは切り出せなくなってくる。"
    T "Seeing her like that, I can't bring up the subject of boarding school again. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:343
translate english gakuen_op_1_da0676a2:

    # T "姉さんの認めるような全寮制の学校となると、その学校にしかないような特色あるカリキュラムを持った、特別な学校ということになるだろう。"
    T "For my sister to accept a boarding school, it would have to be a special school with a particular curriculum found only there. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:349
translate english gakuen_op_1_877bc007:

    # T "（そんな都合のいい学校があるかしら……）"
    T "(Is there a convenient school like that... )"

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:355
translate english gakuen_op_1_54bb21ee:

    # T "「そうね、そうするわ」"
    T "\"Yes, I'll do that. \""

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:361
translate english gakuen_op_1_4490f9ef:

    # T "姉さんにそう返事を返しながら、私は喉元までこみ上げた溜息を飲み込んだ。"
    T "Replying to my sister, I swallow the sigh rising from my throat. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:385
translate english gakuen_op_1_f4c013e7:

    # T "姉さんはまだ時間がある、とは言っていたものの、それでも時間は着々と進んでいく。"
    T "Though my sister had said there was still time, time continues to gradually advance. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:391
translate english gakuen_op_1_d4ea86f7:

    # T "私が進路を決断しなければならない日は、確実に迫ってきている。"
    T "The day where I've got to decide on my course is definitely coming near."

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:397
translate english gakuen_op_1_793676ce:

    # T "そんな中、私はいくつか候補として、全寮制の学校の資料と通学圏内の学校の資料を取り寄せたのだが……。"
    T "I've gathered materials on some boarding schools and schools I can commute to, but... "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:403
translate english gakuen_op_1_a3f207ed:

    # T "結局そのどれも、開いてすらいない状態だ。"
    T "In the end, I haven't even opened them. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:409
translate english gakuen_op_1_9eecd664:

    # T "最終的にどこを選んでも大丈夫なようにしておく、という建前を逃げ道にして、ひたすら勉強だけを続けている。"
    T "I'm only continuing to study hard, running away by claiming that it'll be fine whichever one I choose in the end. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:415
translate english gakuen_op_1_1e595b31:

    # T "（これって……、立派な現実逃避よね。\n 今勉強しても、進路が決まるわけでなし……）"
    T "(This is... a fine way of avoiding reality. \n
Even if I study now, it's not a decision.)"

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:422
translate english gakuen_op_1_3ad43b42:

    # T "（現実逃避といえば……、私は家から出たいだけなのかしら。\n 勝手な独立心で、姉さんを困らせている？）"
    T "(Speaking of running away from reality... maybe I only want to leave the house. \n
Am I being self-centered and making trouble for my sister?)"

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:429
translate english gakuen_op_1_f65b4524:

    # T "（…………）"
    T "(....)"

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:435
translate english gakuen_op_1_a7d723d6:

    # T "（……駄目だ。\n このままだと、時間だけが過ぎて、このまま家にいることになっちゃう）"
    T "(....No. \n
If I stay like this, the time will pass and I'll end up staying here.)"

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:442
translate english gakuen_op_1_9088070c:

    # T "そんな状況を打破するきっかけが我が家に訪れたのは、ある休日の昼下がりのことだった。"
    T "The opportunity to break out of this situation visited my house one holiday afternoon."

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:458
translate english gakuen_op_1_5a66ddb9:

    # T "「は～い」"
    T "\"Ye~s.\""

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:465
translate english gakuen_op_1_e7a123f3:

    # T "今思えば、私はそのときにしっかりと来客が誰であるのかを確認しておくべきだったのだ。"
    T "Thinking about it now, I should have checked to see who the visitor was. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:471
translate english gakuen_op_1_a065177c:

    # T "いっそのこと、チャイムを聞こえなかったことにしてしまった方がよかったのかもしれない。"
    T "Or better yet, I should have pretended not to hear the doorbell. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:477
translate english gakuen_op_1_154c3935:

    # T "……しかし、私は、確認を怠った。"
    T "...However, I neglected to check."

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:483
translate english gakuen_op_1_2bd37727:

    # T "安全な地域だからといって、無用心すぎる。\n 郵便配達だと思ったからなんて、言い訳にもならない。"
    T "Though it's a safe area, I was too careless. \n
I can't excuse myself by saying I thought it was the mail. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:490
translate english gakuen_op_1_5654fd98:

    # T "私は現実主義者。\n 実際に起こったことは否定できないのだ。"
    T "I'm a realist. I can't deny what actually happened. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:497
translate english gakuen_op_1_9e50ccc5:

    # T "私はドアを開け、結果として、それが私の人生を大きく変えてしまった。"
    T "I opened the door, and as a result of that, my life was greatly changed."

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:507
translate english gakuen_op_1_7c08276d:

    # T "「どちら様ですか？」"
    T "Who is it?"

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:519
translate english gakuen_op_1_9910484c:

    # Peter "{size=+20}「[firstname]！！」{/size} "
    Peter "{size=+20}[firstname]!!{/size} "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:525
translate english gakuen_op_1_1d89f351_1:

    # T "「…………」"
    T "...."

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:535
translate english gakuen_op_1_15fd0a5c:

    # voice pet_r0000
    # Peter "「どうしたんですか、[firstname]！無言でドアを閉めようとするなんて！！\n ああ、照れているんですね？相変わらず可愛い人ですね、あなたは！」"
    voice pet_r0000
    Peter " What's wrong, Alice?! Shutting the door without saying a word?!! \n
Ah, you're embarassed? You're always so cute!"

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:543
translate english gakuen_op_1_df8364ce:

    # T "無言でドアを閉めようとしたところ、相手も慣れたように閉じかけたドアの隙間に靴先をねじ込んできた。"
    T "While I was trying to shut the door, the visitor wedged his foot in it, with a practiced air. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:549
translate english gakuen_op_1_3457006f:

    # T "（……ちっ）"
    T "(...tsk)"

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:558
translate english gakuen_op_1_9b13319c:

    # voice pet_r0001
    # Peter "「ああ、愛しい人！\n そんなに照れないでください！」"
    voice pet_r0001
    Peter "Aah, my beloved! \n
Please don't be so shy!"

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:566
translate english gakuen_op_1_53005f35:

    # T "「照れていない。\n 呆れているの」"
    T "\"I'm not being shy. I'm disgusted. \""

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:573
translate english gakuen_op_1_ab222dba:

    # T "なにやら甘ったるいことを言っているような気がするが、私とこの男の間にそんな関係が成立したことは、これまでに一度たりともない。"
    T "He may be saying sweet things, but this man and I have never had even once a relationship like that. "

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:579
translate english gakuen_op_1_a209b61e:

    # T "「……いつ会っても、あんたって変わらないわね」"
    T "\"...Like always, you haven't changed.\""

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:588
translate english gakuen_op_1_714778ae:

    # voice pet_r0002
    # Peter "「ええ！僕はいつでもどこでもあなたを愛していますよ！\n いくら離れようとも、この想いは変わりっこありません！」"
    voice pet_r0002
    Peter "Yes! I am always in love with you, wherever I am! \n
No matter how far apart we are, these feelings won't change!"

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:596
translate english gakuen_op_1_ce812bda:

    # T "「……変わってほしいな。\n せっかく離れていたんだし……」"
    T "\"...I'd like them to change. \n
Since you've gone away.\""

# game/gakuen_op1.rpy:603
translate english gakuen_op_1_d3451504:

    # T "この男、ペーター＝ホワイトはかなり好意的な言い方をすると、私の幼馴染にあたる。"
    T "This man, Peter White, is my childhood friend, although that's a rather favorable way of saying it. "

